Sure, here are some example sentences in Serbian that use the word "utakmica" in different forms and positions:

1. Gledam *utakmicu* na televiziji. (I'm watching a *match* on TV.)
2. Sin moj igra *utakmicu* u subotu. (My son is playing a *match* on Saturday.)
3. Pobedili smo u poslednjoj *utakmici*. (We won the last *match*.)
4. Uživam u gledanju fudbalskih *utakmica*. (I enjoy watching football *matches*.)
5. Ovo je ključna *utakmica* za naš tim. (This is a crucial *match* for our team.)
6. Oni su pobedili u prethodnoj *utakmici*. (They won the previous *match*.)
7. Zašto ne idemo na *utakmicu* zajedno? (Why don't we go to the *match* together?)
8. Fudbalska *utakmica* je bila otkazana zbog lošeg vremena. (The football *match* was canceled due to bad weather.)
9. Odigrali smo dobro u prvoj *utakmici* sezone. (We played well in the first *match* of the season.)
10. Naš tim će igrati protiv rivala u sledećoj *utakmici*. (Our team will play against a rival in the next *match*.)

Note: The *word* "utakmica" in each sentence is emphasized with an asterisk (*) for clarity.